---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
  class="mt-32 w-full bg-surface border-t border-border overflow-hidden relative"
>
  <!-- Interactive / Decorative background glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-[1200px] h-[500px] bg-primary/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none -translate-y-1/2 z-0"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 pt-24 pb-12">
    <!-- CTA prominent: Perfect place since we removed it from Header -->
    <div
      class="bg-bg border border-border p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[var(--radius-3xl)] mb-28 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 shadow-sm group hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors duration-500"
    >
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <h3
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-black tracking-tight text-primary mb-4"
        >
          Ayúdanos a construir.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Este espacio prospera gracias a mentes inquietas. Únete a nosotros
          como escritor, investigador o aportando código y diseño (Open Source).
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/colaborar"
        class="btn shrink-0 text-lg px-8 py-4 flex items-center gap-3"
      >
        Súmate como colaborador
        <div
          class="i-ph-arrow-right-bold group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
        >
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-16 md:gap-8 mb-24">
      <!-- Brand Statement -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-5">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="text-3xl font-display font-black tracking-tighter text-primary inline-block mb-6 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity"
        >
          Cristianamente.
        </a>
        <p
          class="text-text-muted font-serif italic text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-sm mb-8"
        >
          Explorando las intersecciones entre la fe, el asombro filosófico y la
          belleza artística, buscando una cosmovisión holística.
        </p>

        <!-- Socials -->
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/lfreyes97/cristiana"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="GitHub"
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-border-subtle flex items-center justify-center text-text-muted hover:text-primary hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <div class="i-ph-github-logo-duotone text-xl"></div>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/rss.xml"
            aria-label="RSS Feed"
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-border-subtle flex items-center justify-center text-text-muted hover:text-primary hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <div class="i-ph-rss-simple-duotone text-xl"></div>
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:hola@cristianamente.xyz"
            aria-label="Contacto"
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-border-subtle flex items-center justify-center text-text-muted hover:text-primary hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <div class="i-ph-envelope-simple-duotone text-xl"></div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Links: Read -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-3 md:col-start-7 text-left">
        <h4
          class="text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-text-muted mb-6"
        >
          Explorar
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-bold text-sm">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/blog"
              class="text-text hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-2 inline-block transition-transform duration-300"
              >Ensayos y Artículos</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/notes"
              class="text-text hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-2 inline-block transition-transform duration-300"
              >Notas Vivas</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/citas"
              class="text-text hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-2 inline-block transition-transform duration-300"
              >Colección de Citas</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Links: Project -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-3 text-left">
        <h4
          class="text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-text-muted mb-6"
        >
          El Proyecto
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-bold text-sm">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/about"
              class="text-text hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-2 inline-block transition-transform duration-300"
              >Nuestra Filosofía</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/colaborar"
              class="text-text hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-2 inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition-transform duration-300"
            >
              Contribuir <div class="i-ph-arrow-up-right text-xs opacity-50">
              </div>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/rss.xml"
              class="text-text hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-2 inline-block transition-transform duration-300"
              >Suscripción RSS</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div
      class="border-t border-border-subtle pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6"
    >
      <p
        class="text-[10px] text-text-muted font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-center md:text-left"
      >
        © {year} Cristianamente
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] text-text-muted font-mono uppercase tracking-widest"
      >
        <span>Soli Deo Gloria</span>
        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary/40 rotate-45 shrink-0"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
